{"title":"vue中$router和$route的区别","uid":"790acc55f46c3b55d10e0b545934d524","slug":"vue中$router和$route的区别","date":"2021-04-29T12:44:12.000Z","updated":"2021-04-30T01:49:03.364Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/vue中$router和$route的区别.json","keywords":"html,css,javascript,vue,webpack,react,学习,分享","cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zzwi/mycdn@3.0/source/images/cover9.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"vue中-router和-route的区别\"><a href=\"#vue中-router和-route的区别\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"vue中$router和$route的区别\"></a>vue中<code>$router</code>和<code>$route</code>的区别</h1><ol>\n<li>router 为VueRouter的实例，相当于一个全局的路由器对象，里面含有很多属性和子对象，例如history对象，跳转方式<code>this.$router.push()</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p><code>this.$router.push</code>会往history栈中添加一个新的记录，所以，当用户点击浏览器后退按钮时，则回到之前的 URL;</p>\n<p>当你点击<code>&lt;router-link&gt;</code>时，这个方法会在内部调用，所以说，点击<code>&lt;router-link :to=&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code> 等同于调用 <code>router.push(...)</code></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">声明式</th>\n<th align=\"center\">函数式</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>&lt;router-link :to=&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code></td>\n<td align=\"center\">router.push(…)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>route 相当于当前正在跳转的路由对象，可以从里面获取name,path,params,query等</li>\n</ol>\n<p>打印this.$route得到Object对象</p>\n<p>打印this.$router得到VueRouter对象</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><p>router 可以理解为一个容器，或者说一种机制，它管理一组 route 。简单来说，route 只是进行了 URL 和函数的映射，当接收到一个 URL 之后，去路由映射表中查找相应的函数，这个过程是由 router 来处理的。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>route 便是我们在路由配置文件中定义的一个一个单独的路由，</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// route</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n  path<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">'/user'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">'User'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">component</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"../views/User.vue\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n","feature":null,"text":"vue中$router和$route的区别 router 为VueRouter的实例，相当于一个全局的路由器对象，里面含有很多属性和子对象，例如history对象，跳转方式this.$router.push() this.$router.push会往history栈中添加一个新的...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":707,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":12,"path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":12,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#vue%E4%B8%AD-router%E5%92%8C-route%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">vue中$router和$route的区别</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"zzwi","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zzwi/mycdn@1.0/source/images/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"一个努力更新学习笔记并进行技术分享的前端人","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/zzwi","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/zyyyy20","juejin":""}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"vue-router全局导航守卫","uid":"8a35b705442e193280a5d11e0137d6ac","slug":"vue-router全局导航守卫","date":"2021-04-30T01:59:23.000Z","updated":"2021-04-30T02:08:02.679Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/vue-router全局导航守卫.json","keywords":"html,css,javascript,vue,webpack,react,学习,分享","cover":null,"text":"vue-router全局导航守卫使用全局导航守卫 (router.beforeEach) 实现